                span(style='margin-left: 10px; color: blue') (mg/dL)
            +form-row('glom', 'text', 'glom', 'glom')
              label.col-sm-6.col-form-label(for='glom') GLOM FILT RATE, EST
              .col-sm-5.offset-sm-1
